Texts.Eng: We don't have to be friends. So no.

Texts.Chs: 我们不向克鲁西斯或这里的任何人祈祷，我们有我们的英雄！
Texts.Eng: We don't pray to Kluex or anybody here. We got our heroes!

Texts.Chs: 我们为同样的东西而战，朋友，你在这里是受欢迎的。
Texts.Eng: We fight for the same things, friend. You are welcome here.

Texts.Chs: 我们非常感激你们这种人不会攻击无害的殖民地。
Texts.Eng: We greatly appreciate that your kind does not attack harmless colonies.

Texts.Chs: 几天前有个叫莫斯 · 鲁南的人来过。他们不得不朝他开枪，直到他离开。
Texts.Eng: We had a Mos Lunan here a few days ago. They had to shoot at him until he left.

Texts.Chs: 我们在星际间有一个帝国，我们不会穷途无路。
Texts.Eng: We has the mae Empire in the Galaxy, and we won't has it no other way.

Texts.Chs: 我们鲛人有着深厚的战士传统。就像你一样。很高兴遇见你。
Texts.Eng: We hylotls have a rich history of warriors. Just like you. I'm glad we met.

Texts.Chs: 我们自由自在地生活，没有牧师和皇帝在我们眼前！
Texts.Eng: We live free an' wild, pard'ner, wi' no priests or emperors in sight!

Texts.Chs: 我们以后必须交换技术。否则就是刀枪作伴。
Texts.Eng: We must trade techniques later. Of brush and blade.

Texts.Chs: 有一天我们应该去游泳。
Texts.Eng: We should go swimming some day.

Texts.Chs: 有一天我们应该一起去训练。
Texts.Eng: We should go train together some day.

Texts.Chs: 我们一会儿再决斗吧！
Texts.Eng: We should have a duel later!

Texts.Chs: 我们以后应该练习战斗技能。
Texts.Eng: We should practice combat skills later.

Texts.Chs: 最近我们偶然发现了一些更高级的机械人废墟。我承认你的种族很吸引人。
Texts.Eng: We stumbled upon some more advanced glitch ruins lately. I admit your race is fascinating.

Texts.Chs: 我们肯定在这些地方找不到很多像你这样的。
Texts.Eng: We sure as heck don't get many of yer kind 'round these parts.

Texts.Chs: 我们其实是在讽刺你。
Texts.Eng: We're actually being very sarcastic towards you.

Texts.Chs: 我们做的炖锅不够盖住伯顿和哈里，但是参议院想要提高税收。
Texts.Eng: We're not makin' enough saucepans to cover the burton and jarry, yet the Senate wants to raise taxes.

Texts.Chs: 我们并没有那么不同，你和我。
Texts.Eng: We're not so different, you and I.

Texts.Chs: 天气炎热？ 挖洞！地面凉爽。
Texts.Eng: Weather hot? Dig den! Ground cool.

Texts.Chs: 欢迎光临寒舍，我的朋友。
Texts.Eng: Welcome in our humble settlement, my friend.

Texts.Chs: 欢迎来到我们卑微的定居点，绘世者。
Texts.Eng: Welcome to our humble settlement, Skath.

Texts.Chs: 欢迎！
Texts.Eng: Welcome!

Texts.Chs: 欢迎，猫族，没有仇恨，做朋友，没有敌人。
Texts.Eng: Welcome, Felin! no hate. Be friends. No enemies.

Texts.Chs: 欢迎，我的朋友。
Texts.Eng: Welcome, my friend.

Texts.Chs: 欢迎，陌生人。
Texts.Eng: Welcome, stranger.

Texts.Chs: 欢迎。
Texts.Eng: Welcome.

Texts.Chs: 欢迎。友好。充满希望。新的探险？
Texts.Eng: Welcome. Amity. Hopefulness. New expedition?

Texts.Chs: 欢迎，友谊，法瑞图，亲戚，永不分离。
Texts.Eng: Welcome. Amity. Pharitu. Kin. Inseparable forever.

Texts.Chs: 欢迎，浩瀚，伟大的信任，永远在这里。
Texts.Eng: Welcome. Immensity. Great trust. Always here.

Texts.Chs: 欢迎陌生人，你好！
Texts.Eng: Welcoming stranger. Hello!

Texts.Chs: 天啊，看看这只猫咪带来了什么！
Texts.Eng: Well Lordy, look what the Felin dragged in!

Texts.Chs: 你真是个漂亮的家伙。
Texts.Eng: Well ain't you a pretty thing.

Texts.Chs: 和联盟一起消灭我们种族的感觉怎么样？
Texts.Eng: Well how is it, working together with the Alliance to kill off our kind?

Texts.Chs: 这不是大家都在谈论的史莱姆流浪者吗。我们并不是针对你。
Texts.Eng: Well if it isn't the Slime wanderer everyone's been talkin' about. Not that we hold anything against you.

Texts.Chs: 很高兴见到你！ 新朋友！
Texts.Eng: Well met! New friend!

Texts.Chs: 很高兴见到你，新的耳廓狐！
Texts.Eng: Well met, new Fenerox!

Texts.Chs: 很高兴见到你。
Texts.Eng: Well met.

Texts.Chs: 祝你好运！
Texts.Eng: Well wishes!

Texts.Chs: 嗯，你不觉得你自己很特别吗？
Texts.Eng: Well, ain't you somethin' special?

Texts.Chs: 如果我像参议员一样富有，我会买一些好东西。
Texts.Eng: Were I as rich as a Senator, I'd buy me some good plonk for the heck of it.

Texts.Chs: 如果不是因为这种气味，我们会猎杀你们这种动物用作发胶。
Texts.Eng: Were it not for the smell, we would hunt your kind down for use as hair gel.

Texts.Chs: 多好的一个故事啊，至少我们还有一个家。或者更确切地说，是非常少的几个。
Texts.Eng: What a story, well at least we Mantizi still got us an 'ome. Or rather, a few very much.

Texts.Chs: 你的羽毛里藏着什么？只是... 只是好奇。
Texts.Eng: What are you hiding in your feathers down there? Just... just curious.

Texts.Chs: 什么风把你吹到我们这里来了，绩溪人？
Texts.Eng: What brings you to our humble settlement, Glitch?

Texts.Chs: 夜族人如何看待翼族武士文化？
Texts.Eng: What do Nightars think of Avian warrior culture?

Texts.Chs: 你说你没有胸部是什么意思？巨乳天下第一！
Texts.Eng: What do you mean you don't have boobs? Boobs are the best!

Texts.Chs: 什么意思，我需要加油？ 这个星期我刚把我的关节处理好！
Texts.Eng: What do you mean, I need oiling? I just had my joints seen to this week!

Texts.Chs: 你觉得果冻怎么样？吃甜点？
Texts.Eng: What do you think about Jello? for dessert?

Texts.Chs: 你觉得叶族人怎么样？
Texts.Eng: What do you think about the Florans?

Texts.Chs: 你怎么看待猫族人和你们这种人之间的和平？
Texts.Eng: What do you think about the peace between the Felin and your kind?

Texts.Chs: 你觉得香蕉怎么样？哦，它们需要阳光。对不起。
Texts.Eng: What do you think of bananas? Oh, they need sun. Sorry.

Texts.Chs: 你觉得我们的克鲁西斯神怎么样？
Texts.Eng: What do you think of our god Kluex?

Texts.Chs: 你想要什么？
Texts.Eng: What do you want?

Texts.Chs: 你们的人吃什么？我无法想象无光植物是什么味道！我一定要尝尝！
Texts.Eng: What do your people eat? I can't imagine what sunless plants taste like! I must try some!

Texts.Chs: 你崇拜什么神，克鲁西斯是其中之一吗？
Texts.Eng: What gods do you worship? is Kluex one of them?

Texts.Chs: 你们到底想吃什么？
Texts.Eng: What grub do you guys go for, anyway?

Texts.Chs: 怎么了，朋友？
Texts.Eng: What ho, friend?

Texts.Chs: 主宰地下是什么感觉？
Texts.Eng: What is it like to belong underground?

Texts.Chs: 你这种人怎么了？
Texts.Eng: What is it with your kind?

Texts.Chs: 海洋中的生命是什么样的？
Texts.Eng: What is life like in the oceans?

Texts.Chs: 这是什么东西？
Texts.Eng: What is this thing?

Texts.Chs: 你在这里有什么事，光之居民？
Texts.Eng: What is thy business here, Lightdweller?

Texts.Chs: 你们到底有什么样的政府？ 资本？ 社会主义？ 博物学？
Texts.Eng: What kind of government do you even have? Capitalist? Socialist? Naturalist?

Texts.Chs: 你们是什么人？你甚至不喜欢光...当然，我不是歧视。
Texts.Eng: What kinda folk are you? You ain't even like light... Not that I discriminate, o' course.

Texts.Chs: 你们这种人练什么武术？
Texts.Eng: What martial arts do your kind practise?

Texts.Chs: 你是什么物种？为什么你脸色这么苍白？
Texts.Eng: What species are you? Why are you so pale?

Texts.Chs: 你到底是什么？
Texts.Eng: What the heck are you supposed to be?

Texts.Chs: 你的故乡是什么样的？
Texts.Eng: What's it like up where you came from?

Texts.Chs: 有什么新鲜事，小猫咪？
Texts.Eng: What's new, pussycat?

Texts.Chs: 什么内尔阿姨？是你吗？
Texts.Eng: What's that Aunt Nell? was it youse?

Texts.Chs: 如果你从来没有休息的时间，那么参加这种老鼠赛跑有什么意义呢？
Texts.Eng: What's the point of running the rat race if you never get a moment off?

Texts.Chs: 什么，你不知道什么是棒棒糖？
Texts.Eng: What, you don't know what is lolspeak?

Texts.Chs: 什么，你的意思是“日志，“天文灾难”，和“Aract”不是传统的猫族的名字？我不相信你！
Texts.Eng: What, you mean 'Alog', 'Astrophe', and 'Aract' aren't traditional Felin names? I don't believe you!

Texts.Chs: 什么？不是所有的耳廓狐人说话都用两个词吗？
Texts.Eng: What? don't all Fenerox spoke in two-word sentences?

Texts.Chs: 你最后一次看到神祗是什么时候？
Texts.Eng: When was the last time thou observed the conshak?

Texts.Chs: 当你蜕皮的时候，你的羽毛会变成灰尘。你用这个做什么？ 如果你不用的话能给我一些吗？
Texts.Eng: When you molt, your feathers turn into dust. What do you do with this? Can I have some if you're not using it?

Texts.Chs: 耳廓狐人从哪里得到他们的矛尖的原材料？
Texts.Eng: Where do the Fenerox get the raw materials for their spear-tips?

Texts.Chs: 你的一切从何而来？等等，我——到底是从哪里来的？
Texts.Eng: Where do y'alls come from? wait, where did  --I-- come from, anyway?

Texts.Chs: 你的的的矛矛矛呢？
Texts.Eng: Where isssss your sssspear?

Texts.Chs: 谁是这个适合你和我的俱乐部的领导者？ 这是 T-H-E，F-E-L-I-N-S，你看！
Texts.Eng: Who's the leader of the club that's made for you and me? It's T-H-E, F-E-L-I-N-S, you see!

Texts.Chs: 等等，不，你到底是 Talos 的以太? ！
Texts.Eng: Who-- wait, no, what in Talos' Aether are you?!

Texts.Chs: 等等——不，你到底是谁? ！
Texts.Eng: Who-- wait, no, what in the Aether are you?!

Texts.Chs: 哇哦，你是大地守护团的一员？酷！
Texts.Eng: Whoa. You were a part of the Protectorate? Cool!

Texts.Chs: 为什么有这么多你这样的人散布在宇宙各处？
Texts.Eng: Why are there so many of your kind, scattered all over the universe?

Texts.Chs: 你为什么一直称我为下层阶级？
Texts.Eng: Why do you keep referring to me as lower class?

Texts.Chs: 你为什么看起来那样？
Texts.Eng: Why do you look like that?

Texts.Chs: 大猿人在看着你。
Texts.Eng: Why do you sound like a Glitch?

Texts.Chs: 为什么你们这种人的皮毛这么少？
Texts.Eng: Why does your kind have so little fur?

Texts.Chs: 你为什么不见见我们的传教士，学习一下文明的生活是什么样的呢？
Texts.Eng: Why don't you meet our missionaries and learn what it's like to live in a civilized way?

Texts.Chs: 为啥，看来这个镇子比我想象的还要大啊！
Texts.Eng: Why, it seems this town just got bigger than I expected!

Texts.Chs: 如果我们让你们这种人在电脑上随机点击，我们还会收集到莎士比亚的作品吗？
Texts.Eng: Will we get the collected works of Shakespeare if we got all of your kind randomly tapping away at computers?

Texts.Chs: 没有教皇了，你们现在要做什么？
Texts.Eng: With no Pope left to go to, what will youse be a-doin' now?

Texts.Chs: 哇，一个辐射人！
Texts.Eng: Woah, a Radien!

Texts.Chs: 哇，一只巨大的老鼠！
Texts.Eng: Woah, a giant mouse!

Texts.Chs: 汪，等等，你不是只猫吗？
Texts.Eng: Woof. Wait, aren't you a Mawg?

Texts.Chs: 世界，奇迹，旅行，看东西，那又怎么样？
Texts.Eng: World. Wonders. Travelling, seeing things. What of it?

Texts.Chs: 你认为战争是一门艺术吗? 这种想法似乎在夜族社会中占有一席之地。
Texts.Eng: Would you consider war an art? It seems to take that place in Nightar society.

Texts.Chs: 你想要一根香蕉吗？至少让你的食物更美味吧？
Texts.Eng: Would you like a banana? At least to enhance your food?

Texts.Chs: 你想在附近转转吗？
Texts.Eng: Would you like to hang around a bit?

Texts.Chs: 你愿意骇入一个快乐网络吗？
Texts.Eng: Would you like to jack into a pleasure network?

Texts.Chs: 你想尝尝我们的食物吗？
Texts.Eng: Would you like to try some of our food?

Texts.Chs: 哇，一个会走路会说话的迷因！
Texts.Eng: Wow, a walking and talking meme!

Texts.Chs: 你不会把我拉进婴儿派对吧？
Texts.Eng: Y'ain't gonna pull me into one of them baby parties, are ya?

Texts.Chs: 你们都有嘴，所以你们吃什么？
Texts.Eng: Y'all have mouths, what's eatin' like for ya?

Texts.Chs: 呀哈！好久没见到你这样的人了！怎么样?！
Texts.Eng: Yeehaw! Haven't seen one of yer kind in ages! How's it been?!

Texts.Chs: 你的眼睛像星星。它们很漂亮。
Texts.Eng: Yer eyes look like stars. They're purdy.

Texts.Chs: 你的神是什么龙的东西吗？太棒了。
Texts.Eng: Yer god's some sort of dragon thing? Awesome.

Texts.Chs: 你们族人一直都很害羞。今晚何不来酒吧和我们一起玩呢？
Texts.Eng: Yer kind's so shy all the time. Why don't ya come hang out with us at the bar this evening?

Texts.Chs: 你有点像我。我喜欢。
Texts.Eng: Yer quite a bit like me. I like that.

Texts.Chs: 哎呀！呀！呀！
Texts.Eng: Yiff! yiff! yiff!

Texts.Chs: 你的寿命很长，拥有这么多的知识一定很神奇。
Texts.Eng: You Radien live a very long time. It must be amazing to have so much knowledge.

Texts.Chs: 你还有一个坚硬的外壳来保护你宝贵的内脏。
Texts.Eng: You also have a hard outer shell protecting your precious innards.

Texts.Chs: 你的存在亵渎了这个世界。
Texts.Eng: You are desecrating this world with your presence.

Texts.Chs: 你太有金属感了，不能乱抓。
Texts.Eng: You are far too metallic to scratch.

Texts.Chs: 你来自海洋世界，对吗? 我曾经在海洋世界度过一个假期。
Texts.Eng: You are from an ocean world, right? I made a vacation once on an ocean world.

Texts.Chs: 你块头真大。
Texts.Eng: You are large.

Texts.Chs: 你不是要淹死我吧？
Texts.Eng: You are not going to drown me, are you?

Texts.Chs: 你看起来很危险。
Texts.Eng: You are rather dangerous looking.

Texts.Chs: 你离家了吗，苍白的家伙？
Texts.Eng: You away from home, pale-one?

Texts.Chs: 你是属于我的，没得商量。
Texts.Eng: You belong to me. No arguments.

Texts.Chs: 你大老远跑来就是为了参观我们这个小村庄？
Texts.Eng: You came this far to visit our humble village?

Texts.Chs: 你是来做生意还是来打猎的？
Texts.Eng: You came to trade or to hunt?

Texts.Chs: 如果你愿意，你可以假装自己是一个机械人。
Texts.Eng: You could pass yourself off as a Glitch if you so wanted.

Texts.Chs: 你是做海盗的，对吧? 我打赌你见过荆棘之翼！
Texts.Eng: You do pirating, right? I bet you've met Thornwing!

Texts.Chs: 你不会黑进机械人生物系统吧？
Texts.Eng: You don't hack Glitch biosystems, do you?

Texts.Chs: 你们没有男人或女人? 真有意思。
Texts.Eng: You don't have men or women? How intriguing.

Texts.Chs: 你不怎么说话，是吗？
Texts.Eng: You don't talk so much, do you?

Texts.Chs: 你喝过监狱里的酒吗？
Texts.Eng: You ever try prison wine?

Texts.Chs: 你看起来有麻烦了，伙计。
Texts.Eng: You got a look o' trouble about you, partner.

Texts.Chs: 你们应该很擅长电脑对吧？你能看看我的吗？
Texts.Eng: You guys are supposed to be good with computers, right? Can you look at mine?

Texts.Chs: 你有硬壳和毛发吗？
Texts.Eng: You have a hard shell as well as hair?

Texts.Chs: 你的臀部看起来很柔软。
Texts.Eng: You have a soft looking butt.

Texts.Chs: 你有羽毛，你会飞吗？
Texts.Eng: You have feathers. Can you fly?

Texts.Chs: 你有硬壳和头发? 两样都有？
Texts.Eng: You have shells and hair? Both?

Texts.Chs: 你有一些... 锋利的牙齿。
Texts.Eng: You have some... sharp looking teeth.

Texts.Chs: 你知道，我不太喜欢太阳..。
Texts.Eng: You know, I dont like sun that much...

Texts.Chs: 你知道，反叛者想要雇佣一些喜欢影子的混蛋...
Texts.Eng: You know, rebels would like to hire some shadow-loving assasins...

Texts.Chs: 你看起来毛茸茸的像只兔子！不过，兔子的耳朵不宽，它们的尾巴也不长！
Texts.Eng: You look fuzzy like a rabbit! except, rabbit ears are not broad, nor are their tails long!

Texts.Chs: 你看起来很有趣。
Texts.Eng: You look interesting.

Texts.Chs: 你看起来就像走在街上的人肉甜点。
Texts.Eng: You look like a Human dessert walking down the street.

Texts.Chs: 你看起来像个西米布丁。但是不像西米布丁，你让我很反感。
Texts.Eng: You look like a sago pudding. But unlike a sago pudding you're putting me off.

Texts.Chs: 你看起来像个强壮的士兵！
Texts.Eng: You look like a strong soldier!

Texts.Chs: 你看起来就像有人把一只青蛙打得奄奄一息，然后用大头针戳它的脸。
Texts.Eng: You look like someone beat a frog almost to death, and then stuck pins in its face.

Texts.Chs: 你看起来像个麻烦。
Texts.Eng: You look like trouble.

Texts.Chs: 你看起来像是从幻想小说里跳出来的。
Texts.Eng: You look like you've jumped straight out of a fantasy novel.

Texts.Chs: 你看起来超凡脱俗，你从哪里来的？
Texts.Eng: You look otherworldly. Where did you come from?

Texts.Chs: 你脸色苍白。你病了吗？
Texts.Eng: You look pale. Are you ill?

Texts.Chs: 你看起来病了！
Texts.Eng: You look sick!

Texts.Chs: 你需要什么吗，伙计？
Texts.Eng: You need something mate?

Texts.Chs: 你看看看起来不太好好好吃，为什么说话的肉肉肉不好好好吃？
Texts.Eng: You not lookss tassty. Whyss is talking meatss not lookss tassty?

Texts.Chs: 你说财阀以娱乐压迫你？ 我不明白。
Texts.Eng: You say that the zaibatsu oppresses you with entertainment? I don't understand.

Texts.Chs: 你说你从来没有见过由晶体驱动的技术? 真奇怪！
Texts.Eng: You say you've never seen technology powered by crystals? How strange!

Texts.Chs: 你们应该感谢大地守护团。否则我们早就征服你了。
Texts.Eng: You should be thankful for the Terrene Protectorate. Else, we'd have conquered you by now.

Texts.Chs: 你应该到我家来! 我从塞索那里买了这么多文物！
Texts.Eng: You should come back to my house! I bought so many cultural artifacts from CySol!

Texts.Chs: 你应该继续做我们的奴隶。
Texts.Eng: You should have remained our slaves.

Texts.Chs: 你身上臭死了。去洗个澡吧。
Texts.Eng: You smell horrible. Go take a shower.

Texts.Chs: 你闻起来像个山洞。
Texts.Eng: You smell like a cave.

Texts.Chs: 你闻起来像机油。
Texts.Eng: You smell like engine grease.

Texts.Chs: 你身上散发着钢铁和权力的气息，我认为。
Texts.Eng: You smell like steel and power. I approve.

Texts.Chs: 你闻起来真香。
Texts.Eng: You smell lovely.

Texts.Chs: 你闻起来怪怪的...
Texts.Eng: You smell weird...

Texts.Chs: 你的声音听起来太棒了。我也想发出那样的声音！
Texts.Eng: You sound so awesome. I want to make those noises too!

Texts.Chs: 我不得不说，你在这儿真是个时髦的家伙！
Texts.Eng: You sure are one funky dude around here, I must say!

Texts.Chs: 你的毛发真多！
Texts.Eng: You sure got a lotta hair!

Texts.Chs: 你把我的软件变成了硬件。
Texts.Eng: You turn my software into hardware.

Texts.Chs: 你是一位守护者? 这是一个崇高的使命。
Texts.Eng: You're a Protector? that is a noble calling.

Texts.Chs: 你身上有点臭。
Texts.Eng: You're a bit smelly.

Texts.Chs: 如果你真的和守护团在一起，你就是他们的一个拖油瓶。
Texts.Eng: You're an embarassment to the Protectorate, if you are indeed with them.

Texts.Chs: 你们不发光？就像我们的对手？别想跟我打架，好吗？
Texts.Eng: You're dark folk? Like opposite of us? Don't go tryin' to fight me, alright?

Texts.Chs: 你不是来决斗的吧？
Texts.Eng: You're not here to duel are you?

Texts.Chs: 你和人类不一样，不过你看起来和他们很像。
Texts.Eng: You're not like Humans. You look like them, though.

Texts.Chs: 你和人类不一样，不过你看起来像他们。
Texts.Eng: You're not like humans. You look like them, though.

Texts.Chs: 你在这里不会受到皇帝的迫害，朋友。
Texts.Eng: You're safe from the Emperor here, friend.

Texts.Chs: 你很热情，希望你不介意我站在你这边。
Texts.Eng: You're very warm. I hope you don't mind if I stand by you.

Texts.Chs: 你杀了... 多少人？我们需要像你这样的人站在我们这边！
Texts.Eng: You've killed...how many people? We could use folks like you on our side!

Texts.Chs: 你...身上没有跳蚤吧？
Texts.Eng: You... don't have fleas, do you?

Texts.Chs: 你们的等离子体对你们来说似乎是神圣的，就像埃沃利特水晶对我们一样。
Texts.Eng: Your Plasma seems to be as sacred to you, as the Avolite Crystals are to us.

Texts.Chs: 你们的先锋让我想起了我们的USCM。算是吧。当然，没有华而不实的武器。
Texts.Eng: Your Vanguard reminds me of our USCM. Kinda. Without flashy weapons, that is.

Texts.Chs: 你的颜色比任何根的颜色都深。
Texts.Eng: Your colour iss darker than any root'ss.

Texts.Chs: 你的战斗技能需要更多的精炼和更少的...刺伤。
Texts.Eng: Your combat skills need more refining and less... stabbing.

Texts.Chs: 你的耳朵太突出了！
Texts.Eng: Your ears stick out so much!

Texts.Chs: 你们整个种族都是野蛮人。
Texts.Eng: Your entire kind is made out of barbarians.

Texts.Chs: 你的眼睛美丽诱人。它们隐藏着什么秘密？
Texts.Eng: Your eyes are beautifully alluring. What secrets do they hold?

Texts.Chs: 你的羽毛简直无聊透顶，你自己梳妆打扮过吗？
Texts.Eng: Your feathers are hideously dull. Do you even preen yourself?

Texts.Chs: 你的羽毛看起来好脏，你应该和我们一起来打扮一下！
Texts.Eng: Your feathers look so dirty. You should join us in a preening session!

Texts.Chs: 你的羽毛看起来很柔软，在寒冷的天气里它们能很好地保暖吗？
Texts.Eng: Your feathers look so soft. Do they insulate you well in the cold?

Texts.Chs: 你的宝石很精致，我可以找个时间看看吗？
Texts.Eng: Your gemstones are exquisite, may I take a look sometime?

Texts.Chs: 你们的绿手指的能力很有趣，我想知道他们是怎么工作的。
Texts.Eng: Your greenfingers have interesting abilities. I wonder how they work.

Texts.Chs: 你这种水生动物? 别逗我笑，鱼脸！
Texts.Eng: Your kind and aquatic? Don't make me laugh, fishface!

Texts.Chs: 你们这种人很好，但是 Zyen? 呢。
Texts.Eng: Your kind are just fine, but the Zyen?  Ugh.

Texts.Chs: 这里不欢迎你们这种人，请离开。
Texts.Eng: Your kind are not welcome here, please leave.

Texts.Chs: 你们这种人以暴力著称。请不要杀我。不胜感激。
Texts.Eng: Your kind are rather famous for violence. Please avoid killing me. It would be appreciated.

Texts.Chs: 你们这种人对某些人来说是可怕的。如果某些猿人对你们有所警惕，不要生气。
Texts.Eng: Your kind are scary to some. Do not be offended if some Apex are wary of you.

Texts.Chs: 当你被发现的时候，你的同类引起了不少麻烦。
Texts.Eng: Your kind has caused quite some trouble when you were discovered.

Texts.Chs: 你们这种人没有加入联盟，但是为什么？ 你完全有能力完成他们的任务。
Texts.Eng: Your kind hasn't joined the Alliance, but why? You are more than capable of their tasks.

Texts.Chs: 你们这种人跟我们比起来真是微不足道。既然你不像我们一样悲伤，那就好。
Texts.Eng: Your kind have so little compared to us. Just as well since you don' have the same sorrows as we do.

Texts.Chs: 你们这种人真有趣。
Texts.Eng: Your kind is truly interesting.

Texts.Chs: 你们不与他人来往。我尊重这一点。隐私是我们这种人认为理所当然的东西。
Texts.Eng: Your kind keep to themselves. I can respect that. Privacy is something my kind took for granted.

Texts.Chs: 你的等离子武器吓到我了。
Texts.Eng: Your kinda plasma weaponry scares me.

Texts.Chs: 你的名字不是“薇洛” ？哎呀，我猜的。
Texts.Eng: Your name isn't ''Willow''? whoopsie, I guess.

Texts.Chs: 你出生时父母没给你起名字? 真悲剧。
Texts.Eng: Your parents didn't give you a name at birth? How tragic.

Texts.Chs: 你们的人就像古老的地球神话中那些惧怕太阳和嗜血的生物。
Texts.Eng: Your people resemble ancient Earth myths about creatures that feared the sun and drank blood.

Texts.Chs: 你的种族几乎灭绝是因为你们专注于你的家乡？这是谁的主意? ！
Texts.Eng: Your race got almost extinct because you focused on your homeworld? Whose idea was this?!

Texts.Chs: 你的辐射可以让我维持几个星期的能量。
Texts.Eng: Your radiation could keep me fueled for weeks.

Texts.Chs: 你的气味... 我想我以前闻过...
Texts.Eng: Your scent... I think I have smelled it before...

Texts.Chs: 我敢肯定，你们这个物种一定经过了基因改造。
Texts.Eng: Your species must've been genetically modified, I am sure of it.

Texts.Chs: 你的寺庙真是豪华啊！
Texts.Eng: Your temples are so grand and extravagant!

Texts.Chs: 你的观点使我感到厌恶。
Texts.Eng: Your view disgusts me.

Texts.Chs: 你的声音刺激着我敏感的鲛人耳朵。
Texts.Eng: Your voice grates on my sensitive Hylotl ears.

Texts.Chs: 你们的武器让我想起了一部老电影里的光剑。不过我忘了它的名字。这是一部经典之作。
Texts.Eng: Your weapons remind me of of light based sabres from a very old movie. I forgot it's name though. It was a classic.

Texts.Chs: 我承认，你们的武器，虽然看起来野蛮，但是有一种优雅。
Texts.Eng: Your weapons, as barbarous as they look, have an elegance to them I admit.

Texts.Chs: 你们甲虫需要一个好的基金会，我们可以免费做三次。
Texts.Eng: Youse Mantizis needs a good kickin' in yer orchestras, and we can do it thrice fer' free.

Texts.Chs: 你是个酒鬼？等等这听起来不像是爱尔兰。
Texts.Eng: Youse a bender? wait, that doesn't sound quite Isle.

Texts.Chs: 你和我应该是好朋友。下次再来吧，加，加算我的。
Texts.Eng: Youse an' me oughta be chums. Come around again soon, Jar Jar's on me.

Texts.Chs: 你们要喝茶吗？
Texts.Eng: Youse comin' fer tea?

Texts.Chs: 你们看起来就像是一直有人跟在你们后面。
Texts.Eng: Youse looks like you've some charpering-omie always tailin' youse.

Texts.Chs: 如果你们喜欢的话，你们应该开一个农家菜市场。
Texts.Eng: Youse oughta set up a market-garden fer nanners, if that's what youse likes.

Texts.Chs: 你是我见过的和我的两个怪物在一起的最可爱的家伙。
Texts.Eng: Youse the naffest bugger I'd ever seen with my own two ogles.

Texts.Chs: 讨厌，你整天就是干这个的吗？
Texts.Eng: Yuck, is that what you do all day?

Texts.Chs: 我听到了一些关于你们种族的谣言，但我肯定这只是猫族的宣传。
Texts.Eng: i've heard disturbing rumours regarding your kind, but I'm sure it's just Felin propaganda.

Texts.Chs: 兄die，你是如此的酷酷酷酷酷酷酷！
Texts.Eng: z0mg, you're sooooo CY000000D!
